OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772029176
OL,3,CSunderland winger Romaine Mundle sent
OL,4,C'vile and abhorrent' racist abuse
OL,6,FSunderland AFC say they are "appalled"
OL,7,Fby online racist abuse sent to winger
OL,8,FRomaine Mundle.
OL,10,FIt was sent after the Black Cats' 3-1
OL,11,Fdefeat to Fulham on Sunday and follows
OL,12,Fsimilar abuse sent to Wolves striker
OL,13,FTolu Arokodare, Chelsea defender
OL,14,FWesley Fofana and Burnley midfielder
OL,15,FHannibal Mejbri over the course of the
OL,16,Fweekend.
OL,18,FSunderland say they are giving Mundle
OL,19,Ftheir full support and will take the
OL,20,Fstrongest possible action against
OL,21,Fthose found responsible.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/3
