PN,42902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772029176
OL,3,CSunderland winger Romaine Mundle sent
OL,4,C'vile and abhorrent' racist abuse
OL,6,FIn a statement, the club said:
OL,7,F"Sunderland AFC is appalled by the
OL,8,Fvile online racist abuse directed at
OL,9,FRomaine Mundle following today's
OL,10,FPremier League fixture against Fulham.
OL,12,F"The abhorrent behaviour displayed by
OL,13,Fmultiple individuals is unacceptable
OL,14,Fand will not be tolerated by the club
OL,15,Funder any circumstances.
OL,17,F"There is no place for racism in our
OL,18,Fsociety, and we stand with Romaine,
OL,19,Fwho has our full support.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/3
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
