PN,42903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F429A1772029176
OL,3,CSunderland winger Romaine Mundle sent
OL,4,C'vile and abhorrent' racist abuse
OL,6,F"The club is actively working with the
OL,7,Frelevant authorities and online
OL,8,Fplatforms to identify those
OL,9,Fresponsible, and we will take the
OL,10,Fstrongest possible action available to
OL,11,Fus.
OL,13,F"These individuals do not represent
OL,14,FSunderland AFC, our values, or our
OL,15,Fcommunity - and they are not welcome
OL,16,Fon Wearside."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/3
